 special, in the name of the dignity of your exalted majesty, in the name of the greatness of your names, in the name of the purity of your prophets, in the name of the light of your chosen representatives, in the name of the blood shed by the martyrs in your cause, in the name of the ink used by the scholars of your purpose and plan, in the name of the prayers of the righteous and in the name of the invocations made by your servants leaving in resignation and asceticism,We beseech you for continuous addition in knowledge, freedom from sickness in the body, long duration of life spent in your obedience abundance in the means of livelihood, divine guidance to turn repentant unto you, before death, freedom from pain at the time of death, protection after death, light in the grave, escape from the hell, entry into the paradise and safety from all the evils of the world and from the chastisement in the hereafter, in the name and for the sake of Muhammad and his pure, purified and infallible progeny.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "ILAA-HEE BE-AKHAS-SE SEFAATE-KA WA BE I’ZZE JALAALE-KA WA A’ZAME ASMAA-E-KA WA BE-I’SMATE AMBIYAA-E-KA WA BE-NOORE AWLEYAA-E-KA WA BE-DAME SHOHADAA-E-KA WA BE-MEDAADE O’LAMAA-E-KA WA BE-DOAA’-E SOLAHAA-E-KA WA BE-MONAA-JAATE FOQRAA-E-KA NAS-ALOKA ZEYAA-DATAN FIL I’LME WA SEHA-TAN FIL JISME WA TOOLAN FIL U’MRE FEE TAA-A’TEK WA SE-A’TAN FIR RIZQE WA TAW-BATAN QABLAL MAWTA WA RAA-HATAN I’NDAL MAWTA WA MAGH-FERA-TAN BA’DAL MAWTA WA NOORAN FIL QABRE WA NAJAA-TAN MENAN NAARE WA DOKHOO-LAN FIL JANNATE WA AA’FE-YATIM MIN KULLE BALAA-ID DUNYAA WA A’ZAA-BIL AA-KHE-RAT BE-HAQQE MOHAMMADIN WA AHLE BAIYTE-HIT TAYYE-BEE-NAT TAAHE-REE-NAL MA’SOO-MEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اِلٰهِیْ بِاَخَصِّ صِفَاتِكَ وَبِعَزِّ جَلَالِكَ وَاَعْظَمِ اَسْمَائِكَ وَبِعِصْمَۃِ اَنْۢبَیَائِكَ وَبِنُوْرِ اَوْلِیَائِكَ وَبِدَمِ شُهَدَائِكَ وَبِمِدَادِ عُلَمَائِكَ وَبِدُعَائِ صُلَحَائِكَ وَبِمُنَاجَاۃِ فُقَرَائِكَ نَسْاَلُكَ زِیَادَۃً فِی الْعِلْمِ وَصِحَۃً فِیْ الْجِسْمِ وَطُوْلًا فِی الْعُمْرِ فِیْ طَاعَتِكْ وَسِعَۃً فِیْ الرِّزْقِ وَتَوْبَۃً قَبْلَ الْمَوْتَ وَرَاحَۃً عِنْدَ الْمَوْتَ وَمَغْفِرَۃً بَعْدَ الْمَوْتَ وَنُوْرًا فِی الْقَبْرِ وَنَجَاۃٍ مِنَ النَّارِ وَدُخُوْلًا فِی الْجَنَّۃِ وَعَافِیَۃٍ مِّنْ كُلِّ بَلَائِ الدُّنْیَا وَعَذَابِ الْآخِرَۃْ بِحَقِّ مُحَمَّدٍ وَاَهْلِ بَیْتِهِ الطَّیِّبِیْنَ الطَّاهِرِیْنَ الْمَعْصُوْمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, 